ion_count":263},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"# Outlier Detection \n* Bir Verinin Q1 - 1.5IQR lik yada Q3+1.5IQR diliminin dışında kalacak kadar uç ve çıkıntı verilerin analizi anomalileri bulmak için kullanılır","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"# ÖRNEK ÇALIŞMA \n* **Örnek Veri** [2 3 4 5 6 7 8 30]\n\n* **02 MEDİAN = 5.5**\n\n* **Q1 = 3.5**\n\n* **Q3 7.5**\n\n* **IQR = Q3-Q1 = 4**\n\n* **MİNİMUM DEĞER Q1-1.5*IQR => 3.5-1.5*4 => -2.5**\n\n* **MAKSİMUM DEĞER Q3 + 1.5*IQR => 7.5+1.5*4 => 13.5**\n\nSonuç: O zaman -2.5 altındaki değerler datam için anomali 13.5 üstündeki değerlerde datam için anomali","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"def detect_outlier(df, feature):\n    outlier_list = []\n    for c in feature:\n\n        Q1 = np.percentile(df[c], 25)\n\n        Q3 = np.percentile(df[c], 75)\n\n        IQR = Q3-Q1\n        \n        outlier_step = IQR*1.5\n        \n        outlier_list_col = df[(df[c] < Q1 - outlier_step) | (df[c] > Q3 + outlier_step)].index\n        \n        outlier_list.extend(outlier_list_col)\n\n    outlier_list = Counter(outlier_list)\n    multiple_outliers = list(i for i, v in outlier_list. items() if v > 2)\n    return multiple_outliers","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.814606Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.815052Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.829448Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.815021Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.828500Z"}},"outputs":[],"execution_count":264},{"cell_type":"code","source":"train_df.loc[detect_outlier(train_df, [\"Age\", \"SibSp\", \"Parch\", \"Fare\"])]","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.830458Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.831062Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.860331Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.831020Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-13T22:15:41.859566Z"}},"outputs":[{"execution_count":